========================================================
SERVICE COMPARISON TABLES (CORRECTLY FORMATTED)
========================================================

-----------------------------------------------
FOREGROUND SERVICE vs BACKGROUND vs BOUND SERVICE
-----------------------------------------------

+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
| Feature              | Foreground Service   | Background Service   | Bound Service        |
+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
| Runs in background   | YES                  | YES                  | YES                  |
| Notification shown   | YES (Mandatory)      | NO                   | NO                   |
| User aware           | YES                  | NO                   | YES                  |
| High priority        | YES                  | NO                   | NO                   |
| Can be killed        | Rare                 | Very likely          | When unbound         |
| Best for long tasks  | YES                  | NO                   | NO                   |
| UI interaction       | NO                   | NO                   | YES (via binding)    |
+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+

------------------------------------------------
FOREGROUND SERVICE vs WORKMANAGER
------------------------------------------------

+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
| Feature               | Foreground Service   | WorkManager          |
+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+
| Immediate execution   | YES                  | NO                   |
| Long-running          | YES                  | NO                   |
| Guaranteed execution  | YES                  | YES                  |
| Needs notification    | YES                  | NO                   |
| User visible          | YES                  | NO                   |
| Best for              | Music, GPS, Calls    | Background sync      |
+-----------------------+----------------------+----------------------+

